Okay. So Otter Weekend is this weekend coming up Saturday and Sunday it's from 10 to 4.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:58.110
And it's free to admission. So you just pay your
admission and you get to do the activities and

00:01:58.110 --> 00:02:02.070
